    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering 333 hp via individual throttle bodies and a high-strung 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent compression across all cylinders. The chassis benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the variable M-differential translates power effectively through the corners. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, addressing key preventative service items for this high-revving platform. Finished in classic Carbon Black, this example offers a visceral mechanical connection and balanced weight distribution for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
