    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver that perfectly balances performance with everyday practicality. The exterior finish retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot the occasional minor stone chip or faint surface scratch consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is free of tears or significant stains, and all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with recent work including a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension provides a composed, quiet ride. Whether you're navigating daily traffic or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car offers the peace of mind that only comes from a history of responsible ownership. It is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a vehicle that looks great and performs even better.",
      "price": 34500.0,
